<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .interest-details {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1 style="color: #1f2937; margin: 0;">New Interest in Your Property</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= firstName %>,</p>

      <p>We're excited to inform you that someone has shown interest in your property listing!</p>

      <div class="interest-details">
        <p><strong>Interested User:</strong>
          <%= interestedUser.first_name %>
            <%= interestedUser.last_name %>
        </p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong>
          <%= interestedUser.email %>
        </p>
        <p><strong>Message:</strong>
          <%= message %>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>You can view and manage this interest in your dashboard by clicking the button below:</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= appUrl %>/properties/<%= propertyId %>" class="button">
          View Property Details
        </a>
      </div>

      <p>Please respond to the interested party in a timely manner to maintain good communication and increase your
        chances of a successful transaction.</p>

      <p>
        Best regards,<br>
        The GetOnePlot Team
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= year %> GetOnePlot. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>